            "title": "Harvesting Tips",
            "content": "Coconuts are harvested at varying intervals. Tender nuts are harvested at 7-8 months. Mature nuts for copra/oil are harvested at 11-12 months when the husk turns brown. Yield varies from 80-100 nuts/palm/year for good varieties."
